  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>In conversations, people often use phrases like <code>you know what</code> not to ask a real question but to share something important. It's like saying, <code>Listen, I have something to tell you.</code></p>\n<p>For example, if someone says, <code>You know what? I love ice cream,</code> they don't expect you to guess; they are just excited to tell you about their love for ice cream.</p>\n</section>",
